{
  "stem": "15393.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In this case, he wanted-- women and children.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Women and children.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He wanted my mother and me out of the house and into hiding.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he said-- he has a very good document working where he does, where he was working, again, as a carpenter and cabinet maker.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He worked for a German authority this time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he said my papers are very adequate because this is-- he worked for what they called the [NON-ENGLISH], which was, you know, quite an important establishment.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he said nothing is going to happen to me and I stay with the boy.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Child will go to work with me and so on.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You go into hiding.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "My mother didn't want to.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Eventually she condescended and she took me and we went.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My mother wanted my brother to come.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the people where we were going to be hidden, it was next house to where we live, the very next house, there was a shop, and milliners shop.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there were two sisters, two Jewish ladies, who were running the shop.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they said to my mother that they are going to close the shop up and use it as a hiding place, which is absolutely-- when you think about it now, or even later when I thought about, when one thought about it, it was ludicrous because what sort of a hiding place was that?",
      "word_count": 55
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But in once naive state of mind in those days, at the beginning, one thought this was-- shop is closed so there is nobody there.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my mother said, all right.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "May I please come with the two children?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He said, no, and they said, no way, and certainly not the little boy.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He's too young.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He may cry.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Something may happen.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
